org.gvsig.raster.georeferencing.swing

Interface GeoreferencingSwingManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultGeoreferencingSwingManager

    public interface GeoreferencingSwingManager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's swing user interface. It is the swing library's main entry point, and provides all the services to manage library swing components.
    See Also:
    GeoreferencingWindowManager, JValidationServicePanel
